docinfo.macro:
Call Start()
Sub Start()
Dim Start
Start=msgbox("Seandainya Kau Tau Betapa Aku Cinta Padamu",vb+vbinformation," Gondronk Love Rara")
If Start=vbOk Then
Call Ask()
End If
End Sub
Sub Ask()
Dim Ask
Ask=msgbox("Apakah Kau Juga Cinta Padaku ?",vbYesNo+vbquestion,"Gondronk Love Rara")
If Ask=vbYes Then
Call Love()
End If
If Ask=vbNo Then
Call Hate()
End If
End Sub
Sub Love()
Dim Love
Love=msgbox("Oh ... Alangkah Senangnya Hatiku",vb+vbexclamation,"Gondronk Love Rara")
If Love=vbOk Then
Call Owns()
End If
End Sub
Sub Hate()
Dim Hate
Hate=msgbox("Teganya Dirimu Padaku ... Sakitnya Hati Ini",vb+vbcritical,"Gondronk Love Rara")
If Hate=vbOk Then
createobject("wscript.shell").run "RUNDLL32.EXE user.exe,exitwindows"
End if
End Sub
Sub Owns()
Dim Owns
Owns=msgbox("Yogyakarta Aug 29 2002 by GondronK",vb+vbinformation,"GondronK Love Rara")
If Owns=vbOk Then
WScript.Quit
End If
End Sub
